locality: In secondary cloud forest and pastures above Maldonado.

Cerro Golondrinas. Upper Río Gualpí headwaters, north-facing slope beyond (to north of) ridge crest at 2300 m which rises above the settlements of El Carmen and La Primavera. Primary Upper Montane Pluvial Forest.
Road Nono - Vicinte Maldonado near Santa Rosa.
